Detailed Description

Utility class to iterate over set elements.

Member Function Documentation

void ObexTransportSet::Iterator::Advance (   ) 
 

Advance the iterator. This has the effect of making it point to the next available set element. If there is no more element to point at, the iterator will become the invalid iterator.
